{% # Validation - Preset - Columns features v2.0.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v2.0.0 — first real Tier-3 implementation (was a stale scaffold on the old `display: block` harness). token-section is now the real production theme-root grid; harness chrome + block labels from the shared snippets. Fixture already on current block APIs (columns `3`/`stack_below`/`gap`, group `direction`/`gap`, media placeholder), so no fixture reconciliation. Per `validation-contract.md` Tier 3.
  - v1.0.0 — initial scaffold (composition reference; not tracked as a Tier-3 implementation)

  Tier-3 composition validation for the "columns-features" pattern: a 3-column
  grid where each column is a feature group (media + title + richtext stacked).
  Structure: section → columns(3) → 3 × group(column) → media + title + richtext.
  Exercises the deepest cross-block cascade in the corpus:

  - Nested container-query: the columns lay out 3 tracks when the columns'
    OWN inline-size ≥ stack_below (60rem), and collapse to 1 track below it —
    @container against the block's width, not the viewport (3-up on desktop,
    stacked on mobile).
  - Group-within-column nesting: each column's group (direction: column) stacks
    its media / title / richtext via the group's own gap, independent of the
    section rhythm and the columns gap.
  - Two gap scopes compose: the columns track gap (32) and the inner group gap
    (16) are distinct and both apply.
  - Media placeholder fallback inside each feature card (no seeded image).

  Reachable only at /?view=validation--preset--columns-features.
  See `.context/docs/validation.md` + `validation-contract.md` § Tier 3.
{% endcomment %}

{% liquid
  assign color_scheme = section.settings.color_scheme | default: 'scheme-1'
%}

<token-section data-modifiers="theme-root,color-scheme:{{ color_scheme }}">
  {% render 'validation--breadcrumb' %}

  <header class="validation__intro">
    <h1>Composition: columns-features</h1>
    <p>
      A 3-column grid (<code>columns</code>) where each track is a feature <code>group</code> stacking media + title +
      richtext. Tier-3 probes the deepest cascade: the columns' <code>stack_below</code> container-query (3-up when the
      block is wide enough, stacked when not — resize across the column's own 60rem, not the viewport),
      group-within-column nesting, and the two distinct gap scopes (columns track gap vs inner group gap).
    </p>
  </header>

  {% content_for 'blocks' %}

  {% render 'validation--block-labels', section: section %}
</token-section>

{% render 'validation--harness-styles' %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Preset: columns-features",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section--validation--preset--columns-features",
  "blocks": [{ "type": "@theme" }],
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
